quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  22,56,"Zuva iro utongi huchava huri hwaAllah. Vachatonga pakati pavo. Saka avo vakatenda (muIslaam) nekuita mabasa akanaka, vachapinda mumapindu emufaro (Paradhiso)"
  22,57,"Asi avo vakaramba kutenda, uye vakaramba ndima dzedu (dziri muQurâ€™aan), ndivo vachave nemarwadzo anodzikisira (muGehena)"
  22,58,"Uye avo vakatama munzira yaAllah ndokubva vaurawa kana kufa (vega), zvirokwazvo, Allah vachavapa raramo yakanaka (Paradhiso). Uye zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo vanopa raramo yakanaka kukunda vapi vese"
  22,59,"Zvirokwazvo, vachaita kuti vapinde nenzira inovafadza, uye zvirokwazvo, Allah vane ruzivo rwese, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  22,60,"Saizvozvo zvinoitwa. Uye uyo anodzorera (marwadzo) zvinoenderana nemarwadzisirwo aaitwa, uye otadzirwa zvekare, zvirokwazvo Allah vachamubatsira. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoregerera zvikuru"
  22,61,"Nokuti Allah vanopinza usiku mumasikati, uye vanopinza masikati muhusiku. Uye zvirokwazo, Allah ndivo vanonzwa zvese, vanoona zvose"
  22,62,"Nokuti Allah ndivo Chokwadi (Mwari mumwechete vane kodzero yokunamatwa), uye izvo zvinonamatwa (zvidhori, moto, nezvimwe zvakadaro) kunze kwavo, ndezvenhema. Uye zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo vari pamusoro pezvese, uye ndivo mukuru wezvose"
  22,63,"Hauoni here kuti Allah vanotumira mvura kubva kudenga (inonaya), nyika yobva yaevedza (zvirimwa zvopukira)? Zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo vane tsitsi dzose, uye vane ruzivo rwezvose"
  22,64,"Ndivo muridzi hwezvese zviri mumatenga uye zvose zviri panyika. Uye zvirokwazvo, vane upfumi (havana chavanoda kubva kuvanhu), vanofanirwa kurumbidzwa"